# -----------------------------------------------------------------------
# No API key is required for Employment Hero Enterprise plan users.
#
# To authenticate, run:
#   claude login
# ...and sign in with your Employment Hero work account.
#
# WARNING: If ANTHROPIC_API_KEY is set in your shell environment, Claude
# Code will bill against that API key instead of your Enterprise
# subscription. Before using this repo, check and unset it if present:
#
#   echo $ANTHROPIC_API_KEY        # check if it's set
#   unset ANTHROPIC_API_KEY        # unset for the current session
#
# To unset it permanently, remove it from your ~/.zshrc or ~/.bashrc.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------

# Only uncomment this if you are deliberately using a personal Anthropic
# API account (not recommended for team use).
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your-key-here
